  schema={`<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"MTP Group Fulfillment","url":"https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua","telephone":["+380501444645","+380938277767"],"email":"mtpgrouppromo@gmail.com","address":[{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Счастливое, Бориспольский район","addressRegion":"Киевская область","addressCountry":"UA"},{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Белогородка","addressRegion":"Киевская область","addressCountry":"UA"}],"openingHours":"Mo-Su 08:00-20:00","foundingDate":"2015","numberOfEmployees":"50","description":"Фулфилмент-оператор в Киевской области. Два склада: Счастливое 2800 м² и Белогородка 1100 м². 60 000+ отправлений в месяц, 150+ клиентов, OTIF 99.8% даже в блэкауты 2022."}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Главная","item":"https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"О компании","item":"https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ru/about/"}]}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"AboutPage","mainEntity":{"@type":"Organization","name":"MTP Group Fulfillment","foundingDate":"2015","founder":{"@type":"Person","name":"Николай Лящук"},"location":[{"@type":"Place","name":"Склад Счастливое","address":"Счастливое, Бориспольский район, Киевская область"},{"@type":"Place","name":"Склад Белогородка","address":"Белогородка, Киевская область"}]}}</script>`}
>
<Fragment slot="head">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="uk" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ua/about/">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="ru" href="https://www.fulfillmentmtp.com.ua/ru/about/">
